items.name: Front face lighting / 前面ライトアップ
items.description:
(日本語説明は後半にあります)

To improve the "shadow cast on the character's face" phenomenon that often occurs in AI illustrations, this LoRA lights up character's face.

Since using "lighting up" LoRA may result painting and details to be poor, we also provide "detailing up" LoRA to use in combination. To download it, select "Detailing up" in version tabs above this page.

Usage

Apply "Lighting up" LoRA to brighten character's face and upper body. If the brightness is not enough, increase the LoRA weight; if it is too bright, decrease the LoRA weight.

In case lighting up results painting and details to be poor, apply "Detailing up" LoRA. If detailed too much, try reducing the weight to about 0.75 to 0.5 if necessary.

On my HuggingFace repo, you can download more various other LoRAs. please check it out.

https://huggingface.co/JujoHotaru/lora

AIイラストでよく発生する「キャラクターの顔に影が落ちる」現象を改善するため、前面をライトアップできます。

ライトアップ用のLoRAを使用すると塗りが甘くなりディティールが潰れる場合があるため、それを修正するディティールアップ用のLoRAも用意しています。ページ上のバージョン切り替えで「Detailing up」を選択してダウンロードしてください。

使い方

ライトアップ用LoRAを適用すると、キャラクターの顔から上半身が明るくなります。明るさが足りない場合は強度を上げ、明るすぎる場合は強度を下げてください。

ライトアップにより塗りが甘くなったりディティールが下がる場合は、ディティールアップ用LoRAを同時に適用します。標準ではかなり強めに効きますので、必要に応じて0.75～0.5くらいまで強度を下げてみてください。

HuggingFaceリポジトリでは、他にもさまざまなLoRAを公開しています。

https://huggingface.co/JujoHotaru/lora

items.name: Camila Polizzi (politician)
items.description:
Trained with 30 good images (10 repeats) and 59 normal images (2 repeat).

2090 steps

About the character:

Camila Polizzi is a political activist and former mayoral candidate of Concepción, Chile. She is currently being investigated by the Regional Prosecutor’s Office of Biobío for her alleged involvement in corruption crimes for having rented the En Ti Foundation to achieve a $ 250 million agreement with the Regional Government. The case has been called “lingerie case” because among the expenses justified by Polizzi were receipts for purchases of underwear, as well as garments from prestigious brands, dinners in restaurants and delivery vouchers. Polizzi was born in Concepción, where she studied Psychology, but left her university studies after having two daughters. She defines herself as a “self-taught person” and has taken courses in music, theater and other disciplines. She also has a past as a model, a hobby she acquired when she lived in Rosario, Argentina, during 2010. Polizzi’s fame arose in 2019, when she made videos of political satire on her social networks, type “stand up” comedy. The recordings made her a public figure with hundreds of visits, which prompted her to her political aspirations. In 2021 she ran for mayor of Concepción as an independent with a quota from the Broad Front and Comunes. In the election she obtained 6,559 votes, 8.28% of the total electorate, which was the fourth majority and was not elected. Later she ran for deputy for the Radical Party in the New Social Pact coalition, although she also failed. Since 2022 she works in Barrio Norte, which seeks greater security and recovery of spaces.

Some performance comments:

Trained with cyberrealistic. I think the model gives great results regarding portrait images, in average. Not that good with full body images. Best performance in 0.7 to 1 wheigths.

Restore faces is not very useful.

Reliberate works fine too.

Any comment or critique is super welcome :).

items.name: MBE Style
items.description:
What is MBE style?

The original creator of MBE style is a French designer MBE, who released it on the dribbble website at the end of 2015. MBE style evolved from wireframe Q-version cartoon drawings. The design uses larger and bolder strokes. Compared to flat-style illustrations without strokes, it removes unnecessary color block differentiations inside, making it more concise, universal, and recognizable. The bold strokes create a clear separation and highlight the content, simplifying complexity. All icons and works of this type are referred to as MBE style.

Model introduction and recommended parameters:

This is a LoRA model that reproduces the MBE cartoon style. It can easily generate MBE-style UI icons and works with bright colors and bold strokes.

  • Trigger word: MBE_style

  • Model weight: 0.8-1.2

  • CLIP: 2

  • Suggested prompt words: objects, props, please add no humans

  • Recommended resolution: 512*512 or 512*768

  • Recommended large models: AnythingV5, Anything ink, Ghostmix, and other second-dimensional flat illustration base models.

什么是MBE风格

MBE风格的原创作者是法国设计师MBE于2015年年底在dribbble网站上发布，从线框型Q版卡通画演变出来的MBE风格，设计采用了更大更粗的描边，相比没有描边的扁平化风格插画去除了里面不必要的色块区分，更简洁、更通用、易识别。粗线条描边起到了对界面的绝对隔绝，突显内容，表现清晰，化繁为简；所有此类型的图标和作品都被称为MBE风格。

模型介绍及参数推荐

这是一个还原MBE卡通风格的LoRA，可以方便生成MBE风格的UI图标和作品，拥有明亮的颜色和粗大的描边。

触发词：MBE_style

模型权重：0.8-1.2

CLIP : 2

提示词建议：物品、道具类，请添加 no humans

分辨率建议：512*512 或者 512*768

大模型建议：AnythingV5 , Anything ink , Ghostmix 等二次元扁平插画大模型

QQ交流群号：865046791

模型用途声明

1. 您不得将此模型及其衍生版本（如融合模型版本）托管于计划赚取收入或捐赠的网站/应用程序。如果您需要将此模型及其衍生版本用于商业目的（如生成式服务、售卖图片、将图片用于公开发表的文章或出版物等），请通过微信联系本人（swy198781）。

2. 您不得直接售卖由此模型生成的图片，除非您对该图片进行了足够程度的人工修改，使其在法律意义上可以被完全判定为您的个人作品。如果您违反本条，所造成的一切法律后果由您个人承担，请恕本人概不负责。

3. 您不能使用该模型故意制作或共享非法或有害的输出或内容，请您遵守公序良德，将此模型用于积极正面的用途。

items.name: Kohaku-XL
items.description:
Kohaku XL

An anime SDXL model trained on 100kπ images.

Introduction

This model is trained from sdxl-1.0-base and merged with some other anime models to get optimal result.
I'm planing more training on more images (around 1.6M imgs) and some style lycoris models. so now it is just alpha version.

Usage Details

This model is very flexible on resolution, you can use the resolution you used in sd1.x/2.x to get normal result(like 512x768), you can also use the resolution that is more native for sdxl(like 896*1280) or even bigger (1024x1536 also ok for t2i).
negative_XL neg embedding is recommended.

Acknowledgements

Datasets

  • 280k imgs from Mynefactory

  • 30k imgs from cybermeow

Models

  • AIO-FantasticAnimeXXXL

  • CounterfeitXL

  • NekoRayXL

items.name: Riza Wildman [Princess Resurrection / 怪物王女]
items.description:
Riza Wildman from the 2007 anime series. Fluffy paws included!

How to use
Trigger words are "riza wildman". Her default outfit is tagged as "cropped shirt, green pants, belt". Other tags to try is "muscular female", "impossible clothes", "abs", "obliques", "covered nipples" and general tight clothing and tomboy stuff.
She can be prompted with "paws out" by using the tag "animal hands". I tagged them mainly to get rid of them for normal gens so it was more a happy accident the it works to semi-reliably to prompt them on demand. I suspect how well depends on how much monster stuff is in your model though. Note that some models may hook onto the "animal" part of the tag and add ears as well.
Depending on what you're prompting and other factors recommended weight can be anything from 0.6 to 1.0 with higher values making it easier to prompt default outfit or variants of it such as general tight black clothing.

MISC
Dataset of 37 processed and partially manually tagged screencaps trained at 512 resolution trained on NAI.
All images are untouched txt2img upscaled, no inpainting or helper embeddings used for quality transparence, e.g. - things should look even better if you do.
The training was done on a small subset of the artists images, as such the output of this LyCORS is not an accurate representation neither in quality or style of the source material. Go support the artist Tsunagami if you want the good stuff.

items.name: Style by Michele Mikesell
items.description:
INSTRUCTION:

LoRA works best at a resolution of 768. Using negatives and quality enhancing prompts may break LoRA. I haven't tested the effect of refiner, but don't set it to more than 0.5. Simple prompts give a better result. Put LoRA first, then the keyword, then the prompt. Good luck!!!

And, yes, I'd be happy if you post your thoughts and share your results.

Michele Mikesell is a contemporary artist whose work has garnered significant attention in the art world. Born in the United States, Mikesell's artistic journey has been influenced by a myriad of cultures, experiences, and historical narratives. Her paintings are a testament to her unique vision and her ability to weave together different artistic traditions into a cohesive and captivating whole.

Mikesell's style is a harmonious blend of abstract and figurative elements. She often incorporates vibrant colors, bold strokes, and intricate patterns into her pieces, creating a visual tapestry that is both dynamic and evocative. Her work is characterized by its depth and complexity, with each painting telling a story that invites viewers to delve deeper and uncover the layers of meaning hidden within.

One of the defining features of Mikesell's art is her ability to draw inspiration from a wide range of sources. From ancient myths and legends to modern-day pop culture, she seamlessly integrates these influences into her work, producing pieces that are both timeless and contemporary. Her paintings often feature iconic figures, animals, and symbols, each imbued with a significance that resonates with audiences from diverse backgrounds.

Jena Frumes is an American model and social media influencer with around 5M followers on Instagram.

This is a 140-step TI trained on a dataset of 15 images with these settings.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Do you have a specific idea for a TI in mind? Visit my website and let me know.

Building a good prompt with my TIs

You're obviously free to experiment, but bear in mind that my TIs are trained with a more or less fixed phrasing, that normally starts with:

"photo of EMBEDDING_NAME, a woman"

So I recommend always starting your prompt like that and then building the rest of the prompt from there. For instance, "photo of beautiful (j3nafrum3s:0.99), a woman with beautiful hair, curly hair upsweep updo, as a movie star in a (movie premiere), premiere gala, (near a movie theatre), natural skin texture, (elegant {red|yellow|blue|green|black|turquoise} sweater off-shoulder), (suspenders:1.1), 24mm, 4k textures, soft cinematic light, adobe lightroom, photolab, hdr, intricate, elegant, highly detailed, sharp focus, ((((cinematic look)))), soothing tones, insane details, intricate details, hyperdetailed, low contrast, soft cinematic light, exposure blend, hdr, faded, (paparazzi in background), (painted lips:1.1), ((looking straight at the camera:1.1)), (smiling)"
